      "body" : "Here, a similar question with a link on how to overcome the problem: <a href=\"http://stackoverflow.com/questions/14487682/diamond-operator-is-not-supported\" title=\"diamond operator is not supported\">stackoverflow.com/questions/14487682/&hellip;</a>"
