    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Maybe these answers above are old but with the new Android Studios 1, you do the following to see the module to run on 1.7 (or 1.6 if you prefer). Click File --> Project Structure. Select the module you want to run and then under \"Source Compatibility\" and \"Target Compatibility\", select 1.7. Click \"OK\".</p>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/iIi7q.jpg\" alt=\"Project Structure screen of Android Studios 1\"></p>\n"
  }, {
