    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Always use latest SDK version to build:</p>\n\n<pre><code>compileSdkVersion 23\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>It does <strong>not affect runtime behavior</strong>,  but give you latest programming features.</p>\n"
